::Hevn::
       He chuckles lightly to himself.  "No need to worry.  I know why you're 
uncomfortable.  But you're not yet ready to know that.  You just looked like 
you needed someone to care for you right now.  I didn't mean anything by it, 
I assure you."  He releases her and sits back in his chair.
